Package: linkageR
Type: Package
Title: ATAC-seq and RNA-seq based identification of regulatory loci of genes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Canhui", "Li", "cre", "li.canhui@qq.com")
Maintainer:Canhui Li <li.canhui@qq.com>
Description: This R package identifies potential regulatory sites of genes by 
    calculating the correlation coefficients between ATAC seq and RNA seq data 
    samples, and visualizes them to a certain extent.
